        "content": "<p>I've implemented <code>unfold_subtype</code> tactic.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c\">/-</span><span class=\"cm\"> # unfold subtype -/</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">/-- Eliminate `x : { n : T // P n }` from goals and assumptions, and split it into `x : T` and `x.prop : P x`. -/</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">macro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"unfold_subtype\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">ident</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tactic</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">with_unfolding_all</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">all_goals</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mkIdent</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getId</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">++</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`prop</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Subtype</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\